Motion (by

 Senator Faulkner

)—by leave—agreed to:

speech.para:
'9AA.(1) At six monthly intervals the Minister must publish in each State and Territory, in at least two of the newspapers which circulate generally in that State or Territory, a notice in plain English (

 a subsection (1) notice

) setting out the effect of this section and calling for nominations of plant or animal species the export or import of which is not controlled and should be controlled by inclusion in Schedule 1 or 2, as the case may be.
